reviewText: The funniest movie I've seen in a while
very comic I like but you must talk italian

I LOVE this film, I don't understand why in USA was not released, at my knowledge.  Alessandro Siani is great and did a fantastic job here.  I like his others films too, but, il Principe Abusivo it's the Best.  It's a very beautiful story (not new) but made with the heart, a family film for everyone.
